117
0:06:05.995,000 --> 0:06:1,000
They are growing because they have high levels of skills.

118
0:06:11.94,000 --> 0:06:14,000
So when we invest in other people's children,

119
0:06:15.095,000 --> 0:06:19,000
and build up those skills, we increase the overall job growth

120
0:06:19.28,000 --> 0:06:2,000
of a metro area.

121
0:06:20.801,000 --> 0:06:23,000
As another example, if we look

122
0:06:24.689,000 --> 0:06:27,000
