157
0:08:16.208,000 --> 0:08:2,000
to introduce new technology, new production techniques.

158
0:08:20.264,000 --> 0:08:23,000
So as a result, my employer is going to be less productive.

159
0:08:23.866,000 --> 0:08:26,000
